posts.post_title: Looking for higher grade T205 HOF's
posts.post_content:
I've recently begun collecting higher grade T205 hall of famers. I'd prefer the cards to be nicely centered with limited chipping & corner rounding. 

Psa and Sgc examples are welcome in the 4, 5, 6 and 7 graded range.

If you have any available which fit this criteria please drop me a PM or email with what you might have.

Thanks all,

[url]andreatny@q.com[/url]
Well, not a 4 but close....lmk if interested
